{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You are assigned to the recovery unit, Sierra, tasked with recovering derelict rovers from abandoned mining colonies for recommissioning. You and your crew must operate the rover to a designated location for safe aerial retrieval. Navigate through its terrain and return the rover in adequate condition.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3298560/extras/BewareWhatLiesWithin.png?t=1735675381\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Having lacked maintenance for centuries, these rovers long surpassed their mechanical lifespan. Additionally, various life forms\u2014whether hostile or not, intelligent or not\u2014may have found their way inside. While this may prove concerning when operating these rovers, don't let this deter you from your mission.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3298560/extras/RoverInterior.gif?t=1735675381\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3298560/extras/BewareWhatLiesWithout.png?t=1735675381\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">These planets are hazardous and all protective measures were abandoned when <i>The Collective</i> withdrew support for the colonies. The specific hazards vary between planets. Many pose environmental hazards, while others pose [REDACTED] hazards.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3298560/extras/RoverInStorm.gif?t=1735675381\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3298560/extras/OperateAndMaintain.png?t=1735675381\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Driving the rover to its destination will require optimal navigation and careful maintenance. You must ensure that the rover's integrity is healthy and tasks are spread out evenly. The rover is equipped with utilities that may prove useful in handling different hazards and operational challenges.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3298560/extras/RoverCockpit.gif?t=1735675381\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3298560/extras/Features.png?t=1735675381\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Up to a 4 player crew (co-op)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Proximity voice-chat that adapts with its surroundings</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Eerie atmosphere and procedurally generated rover interiors</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Storyline to follow &amp; progression system</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Various creatures that exhibit unique behaviors</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3298560/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1735675381","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3298560/page.bg.jpg?t=1735675381","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3298560/bc0e9e1d16969565995f9cac451aba249209b3cb/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1735675381","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3298560/bc0e9e1d16969565995f9cac451aba249209b3cb/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1735675381","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"Co-op","id":9},{"description":"Online Co-op","id":38},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22}],"